'''Absame''' waa [[Beelaha Soomaalida|qabiil]] ka tirsan beelaha [[Daarood]]ka, ee [[Soomaali|Dadka Soomaalida]]. Absamuhu waa magaca guud ee beelo ka farcama Daaroodka. Kuwaasi waxaa ka mid ah [[Ogaadeen (beel)|Beesha Ogaadeen]] taasi oo deegaan ku ah wadanka [[Soomaaliya]] (gaar ahaan koonfur), [[Itoobiya]] (meelo ka mid ah deegaanka [[Ogaden]]) iyo wadanka [[Kiinya]].<ref>"Collective Punishment", p. 14</ref>

is a sub-clan of the [[Somali people|Somali]] [[Darod]] clan. It is in turn divided into several sub-groups, with members residing in [[Somalia]], [[Ogaden]] in [[Ethiopia]] and northern [[Kenya]].

